<title>USA: Longhorn Steaks settles lawsuit.</title>
<headline>Longhorn Steaks settles lawsuit.</headline>
<dateline>ATLANTA 1996-12-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Longhorn Steaks Inc said on Wednesday that it has reached an agreement in principle to settle a class action securities lawsuit for $1.4 million.</p>
<p>The settlement of the 1994 lawsuit denies any wrongdoing on the part of the company and its directors, Longhorn Steaks said.</p>
<p>The lawsuit accused Longhorn Steaks and its executives of making material misrepresentations concerning the financial condition of the company, the company said.</p>
<p>The company's insurer will fund much of the settlement, Longhorn Steaks said.</p>
